snippet.title: You'll FORGET CATS & DOGS when you see FUNNY KIDS vs FARM ANIMALS! - This is a LAUGH BOMB
snippet.description:
Farm adventures can be funny tho; innocent kids interacting with clumsy farm animals  can cause lots of fun! Fails, reactions, interactions and lots of other fun! You'll just keep laughing and laughing and... laughing all day long after watching this :P So ridiculous, funny and cute! What is your favorite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
